    <item>
      <title>Employees back pain costs an average of 440 dollars (not counting lost productivity) – 2017</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/employees-back-pain-costs-an-average-of-440-dollars-not-counting-lost-productivity-2017/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Jun 2019 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/employees-back-pain-costs-an-average-of-440-dollars-not-counting-lost-productivity-2017/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;integrated-benefits-institutehttpswwwibiweborghealth-and-productivity-impact-of-chronic-conditions-back-pain&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ibiweb.org/health-and-productivity-impact-of-chronic-conditions-back-pain/&#34;&gt;Integrated Benefits Institute&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/attachments/d3.mock.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;image&#34; width=&#34;800&#34;&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/attachments/d3.mock.pdf&#34;&gt;&lt;i class=&#34;fas fa-file-pdf&#34; style=&#34;margin-right: 0.3em;&#34;&gt;&lt;/i&gt;Download the PDF from VitaminDWiki&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&lt;h4 id=&#34;2013-ibi-report-had-a-cost-breakdown-which-included-presenteeism&#34;&gt;2013 IBI report had a cost breakdown which included Presenteeism&lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Based on $514/employee average&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;table&gt;&#xA;  &lt;thead&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;          &lt;th&gt;&lt;/th&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/thead&gt;&#xA;  &lt;tbody&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Sick days:&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;$131&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Presenteeism:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;$83&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Short-term disability&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;$71&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Long-term disability&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;$42&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;      &lt;tr&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;Workers’ compensation&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;          &lt;td&gt;$19&lt;/td&gt;&#xA;      &lt;/tr&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/tbody&gt;&#xA;&lt;/table&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Employees with back pain are absent four more days per year than those without this ailment&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;and have the equivalent of 4.4 more days of presenteeism annually. &amp;quot;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The cost of less work time and presenteeism makes up more than two-thirds of the total cost of low-back pain to employers, according to IBI, a workforce health and productivity research and measurement organization&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
